Fetch GET /commands on first / keystroke (cache result). Detect / at input start. Show popover above input. Filter by prefix match. Keyboard: arrows to navigate, Enter/Tab to complete, Esc to close. Click to select. Insert /<name> + space into input. Dismiss on blur.